o national football team]] (1948\u201360)\n* [[Belgium national football B team]]\n* [[Belgium national youth football team]] (U-15 \u2013 U-21 squads)\n* [[Belgian First Division A]]\n* [[Sport in Belgium]]\n\n==Footnotes==\n{{notelist-ua}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==Bibliography==\n{{refbegin|30em}}\n* {{cite book |last1=Bernhart |first1=Patrick |last2=Houtman |first2=Joost |title=Zo werden wij wereldkampioen |trans-title=That is how we became world champions |language=nl |year=2014 |publisher=Manteau |location=Antwerp |isbn=978-90-223-2972-6 |ref=harv |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=bj5HAwAAQBAJ}} (Unpaginated version consulted online via [[Google Books]]; the particular phrase by [[Pel\u00e9]] can be retrieved with ''[https://books.google.com/books?hl=nl&id=bj5HAwAAQBAJ&q=vriendschappelijke#v=snippet&q=vriendschappelijke%20pele&f=false this search]''.)\n* {{cite book |last=Boin |first=Victor |authorlink=Victor Boin |title=Het gulden jubileumboek van de K.B.V.B. 1895\u20131945. Geschiedenis van de voetbalsport in Belgie en in Belgisch Kongo |trans-title=The golden jubilee book of the R.B.F.A. 1895\u20131945. History of the football sport in Belgium and in Belgian Congo |language=nl |year=1945 |publisher=Les \u00c9ditions Leclercq & De Haas |location=Brussels |ref=harv}} (Numberless page copy consulted online on 25 June 2014 on [http://goaaal.arch.be/index.php?l=nl&page=varia GOAAAL! Voetbalvaria (by RBFA)])\n* {{cite book |last=De Bock |first=Wim |title=Houwaart de Mos Boskamp |language=nl |year=2013 |publisher=Uitgeverij De Buitenspelers |location=Amsterdam |isbn=978-90-71359-69-9 |ref=harv |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=qTp3AAAAQBAJ}} (Numberless book pages consulted online via [[Google Books]])\n* {{cite book |last=de Vries |first=Andr\u00e9 |title=Flanders: A Cultural History |year=2007 |publisher=Oxford University Press |location=New York |isbn=978-0-19-531493-9 |ref=harv |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=QvSovOY_VV0C}}\n* {{cite